PROFESSOR: No, cannot get
it, it's just too much work

00:09:54.280 --> 00:09:55.000
for an electron.

00:09:55.000 --> 00:09:56.650
It cannot do it.

00:09:56.650 --> 00:09:58.800
There are theorems
like that, Elliott

00:09:58.800 --> 00:10:01.846
Lieb, a mathematical
physicist, has proven

00:10:01.846 --> 00:10:03.220
all kinds of these
things, and we

00:10:03.220 --> 00:10:05.650
might discuss some of
that in the homework,

00:10:05.650 --> 00:10:09.410
it's kind of nice stuff.

